<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BMC Towing Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f6f8fb;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #1d4ed8;
      --success: #15803d;
      --warning: #b45309;
      --danger: #b91c1c;
      --nav: #0f172a;
      --nav-text: #e2e8f0;
      --radius: 18px;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .layout {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      background: var(--nav);
      color: white;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .brand {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .brand h1 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 1.55rem;
    }

    .brand p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .nav {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--nav-text);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      display: block;
    }

    .nav a.active,
    .nav a:hover {
      background: rgba(59,130,246,0.18);
      color: white;
    }

    .main {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .topbar h2 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .subtext {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .controls {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .controls input,
    .controls select,
    .controls button {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font: inherit;
      background: white;
    }

    .controls button {
      background: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .stat-value {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .stat-note {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .section-head h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eff6ff;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    th, td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 12px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    th {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .tag.active {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: var(--success);
    }

    .tag.transfer {
      background: #fef3c7;
      color: var(--warning);
    }

    .tag.expiring {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: var(--danger);
    }

    .list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .list-item {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .list-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .list-item span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .footer-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sidebar { display: none; }
      .stats, .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="brand">
        <h1>BMC Towing</h1>
        <p>Fleet dashboard starter based on your current towing list.</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#" class="active">Fleet Overview</a>
        <a href="#">Active Boats</a>
        <a href="#">Transfers</a>
        <a href="#">Renewals</a>
        <a href="#">Expirations</a>
        <a href="#">Historical Lists</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
      <div class="topbar">
        <div>
          <h2>Towing Dashboard</h2>
          <div class="subtext">Current source: Towing List sheet • fields include Boat ID, HIN, FL#, Boat Name, Home Port, Annual Dues, Active, Renewed, Transfer, Exp, and Requested.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="controls">
          <input type="search" placeholder="Search boat name or FL#" />
          <select>
            <option>All Home Ports</option>
            <option>Beach Marine</option>
            <option>Camachee Cove</option>
            <option>Julington Creek West</option>
          </select>
          <select>
            <option>All Statuses</option>
            <option>Active</option>
            <option>Transfer</option>
            <option>Expiring</option>
          </select>
          <button>Refresh List</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="stats">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="stat-label">Total Boats Listed</div>
          <div class="stat-value">122</div>
          <div class="stat-note">Pulled from the current towing list sheet.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="stat-label">Home Ports</div>
          <div class="stat-value">3</div>
          <div class="stat-note">Beach Marine, Camachee Cove, Julington Creek West</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="stat-label">Transfer Notes</div>
          <div class="stat-value">7</div>
          <div class="stat-note">Rows already showing XFR notes.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="stat-label">Current Header</div>
          <div class="stat-value">2.22.26</div>
          <div class="stat-note">Using your latest update date shown on the sheet.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="section-head">
            <h3>Fleet Snapshot</h3>
            <span class="pill">Real column structure</span>
          </div>

          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Boat ID</th>
                <th>Boat Name</th>
                <th>Home Port</th>
                <th>FL#</th>
                <th>Annual Dues</th>
                <th>Status</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>BT10827</td>
                <td>Getting Reel V</td>
                <td>Beach Marine</td>
                <td>FL3379TZ</td>
                <td>$300</td>
                <td><span class="tag active">Active</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>BT10365</td>
                <td>Reel Therapy VII</td>
                <td>Beach Marine</td>
                <td>FL1716UE</td>
                <td>$350</td>
                <td><span class="tag transfer">Transfer</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>BT10356</td>
                <td>Out of Office IV</td>
                <td>Camachee Cove</td>
                <td>FL5528UA</td>
                <td>$300</td>
                <td><span class="tag active">Active</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>BT10367</td>
                <td>Branch Office IV</td>
                <td>Julington Creek West</td>
                <td>FL7064UB</td>
                <td>$300</td>
                <td><span class="tag transfer">XFR Requested</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>BT10452</td>
                <td>(904) Happy Hour V</td>
                <td>Beach Marine</td>
                <td>FL5531UA</td>
                <td>$300</td>
                <td><span class="tag expiring">Marked Transfer / Renewed</span></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="section-head">
            <h3>What to build next</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="list">
            <div class="list-item">
              <strong>Status logic</strong>
              <span>Convert Active, Renewed, Transfer, Exp, and Requested columns into one clean status system so each boat shows a single dashboard state.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="list-item">
              <strong>Port totals</strong>
              <span>Add grouped counts by home port with totals for Beach Marine, Camachee Cove, and Julington Creek West.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="list-item">
              <strong>Expiring soon</strong>
              <span>Turn the Excel expiration date field into a readable date and flag upcoming renewals automatically.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="list-item">
              <strong>Historical compare</strong>
              <span>Use your older Robert and Historical BUS sheets to show what changed from one version to the next.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h3>Notes</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-note">
          This starter is now aligned more closely with your actual workbook instead of placeholder towing tickets. Next, I’d recommend turning this into a live table with filters, summary cards by home port, and color-coded transfer / expiration flags.
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
